## Design Philosophy

### Professional & Clean
- **Minimalist Design**: Removed excessive gradients, shadows, and visual noise
- **Enterprise Standard**: Followed industry best practices from leading service management platforms
- **Content-First**: Information hierarchy prioritizes readability and usability
- **Consistent Spacing**: Using systematic padding and margins throughout

### User-Friendly
- **Intuitive Navigation**: Clear call-to-actions and logical flow
- **Quick Scanning**: Card-based layout allows fast information scanning
- **Accessible**: High contrast ratios and clear typography
- **Responsive**: Works seamlessly across all device sizes

