- Gray-500: #6B7280 (Secondary text)
- Gray-300: #D1D5DB (Borders)
- Gray-50: #F9FAFB (Backgrounds)

Accent Colors:
- Blue-600: #2563EB (Primary actions)
- Green-500: #10B981 (Success states)
- Red-500: #EF4444 (Error states)

Status Colors:
- Green: Completed
- Blue: In Progress
- Yellow: Pending
- Gray: Other states
```

### Typography
```css
Headings:
- Page Title: text-3xl (30px) font-semibold
- Section Title: text-lg (18px) font-semibold
- Card Title: text-base (16px) font-semibold

Body Text:
- Primary: text-sm (14px)
- Secondary: text-xs (12px)
- Labels: text-xs (12px) font-medium uppercase
```

### Spacing
```css
Container Padding: 4 (1rem)
Card Padding: 5 (1.25rem)
Section Margins: 6 (1.5rem)
Element Gaps: 3-4 (0.75-1rem)
```

### Borders & Shadows
```css
Borders: 1px solid gray-200
Border Radius: rounded-lg (0.5rem)
Shadow: shadow-sm (subtle)
Hover Shadow: shadow-md (moderate)
```

